newsitem.title: AUSTRALIA: RTRS - Outlook for Australia entities positive - S&P.
newsitem.headline: RTRS - Outlook for Australia entities positive - S&P.

text.p: Standard & Poor's Corp said it affirmed its AA long-term foreign currency ratings and revised the foreign currency rating outlooks to positive from stable for seven Australia public entities.

The public entities are The Australian Wheat Board, Export Finance and Insurance Corp, Telstra Corp, The New South Wales government, the Queensland government, the Victorian government and the government of Western Australia.
